w.theverge.com/24252575/sony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24252575/sony-ps5-pro-playstation-5-preorder-buy-price-release-date</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T09:04:58-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T09:04:58-04:00</updated><title>谷歌表示，封闭的广告生态系统并不反竞争，只是更安全</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;充满不同产品广告的页面的照片拼贴。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/EYoCD2dVVOPswMEqU4z1H-9akkw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73612180/STK445_ADVERTISING_STK093_GOOGLE_A.0 .jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge、Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;v6Q71c&quot;>;谷歌本周在法庭上借鉴了一本熟悉的剧本，为自己辩护通过提出安全问题来实施反竞争行为。虽然政府声称其锁定广告技术市场是为了赚更多钱，但谷歌的证人表示，更封闭的生态系统对于用户来说往往更安全——这与谷歌和苹果对其移动应用商店的辩护相呼应。&lt;/p>; &lt; p id=&quot;mthekO&quot;>;谷歌的律师在过去几天里一直在针对司法部进行辩护。该公司辩称，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/24/24253293/google-ad-tech-antitrust-trial-doj-case&quot;>;司法部将其行为视为反竞争行为&lt;/a>; — 例如&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/11/24241386/former-news-corp-executive-google-doj-ad-tech-Trial&quot;>;锁定客户其服务&lt;/a>;并发挥&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/9/24240386/google-doj-ad-tech-antitrust-trial-court-day-one&quot; >;通过其主导地位控制行业规则&lt;/a>;——实际上有正当的商业目的。要点...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253523/google-close-ad-ecosystem-awbid-ad-fraud-3ve &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253523/google-closed-ad-ecosystem-awbid-ad-fraud-3ve" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253523/google-close-ad-ecosystem-awbid-ad-fraud-3ve</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T09:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T09:00:00-04:00</updated><title>徕卡推出第二款Q3相机，配备新镜头，价格更高</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Leica Q3 43 和 Leica Q3 的俯视图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/I30189kvSetY3unmMLHgJk6eucA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73612110/19084_Leica_Q3_43_Ambient_09_HiRe s_crop.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;现在有两个了！&lt;/em>; |图片：徕卡相机&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;YeKv2R&quot;>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;SSRlmK&quot;>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;QC5bvW&quot;>;徕卡Q系列全系列自 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2015/6/10/8754047/leica-q-camera-announcement-price-hands-on- launch&quot;>;最初是在 2015 年&lt;/a>;，但现在该公司正在进行重组。今天推出的徕卡 Q3 43 与 60 兆像素几乎相同 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/5/25/23736639/leica-q3-camera-28mm-fixed-lens-compact -8k-availability-price-specs&quot;>;Q3&lt;/a>;，但它配备了 43mm f/2 镜头，视野更窄，更适合特写和肖像——当然，它更贵，价格为 6,895 美元，而标准型号为 6,295 美元。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;UGpTcZ&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot; readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Fujifilm X100VI vs. Ricoh GR IIIx：最佳傻瓜相机之战&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/24118170/fujifilm-x100vi-ricoh-gr-iiix-point-shoot-camera-comparison&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;制造相机的打印机公司再打印一个版本&quot;, &quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24158218/ricoh-gr-iii-hdf-full-frame-video&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;MH3qyA&quot;>;Q3 43 的规格基本相同，因为它基本上是一款 Q3 相机，永久安装了新的非球面 APO-Summicron 43mm f/2 镜头和灰色人造革（我想财力雄厚的用户不可避免地会同时购买这两款相机）可以区分它们在袋子里）。它使用相同的背照式传感器...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254024/leica-q3-43-full -frame-fixed-lens-43mm-camera-price-specs&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254024/leica-q3-43-full-frame-fixed-lens-43mm-camera-price-specs" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24254024/leica-q3-43-full-frame-fixed-lens-43mm-camera-price-specs</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T08:40:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T08:40:00-04:00</updated><title>克里斯汀·贝尔 (Kristen Bell) 在成为 Instagram 官方代言人之前告诉 Instagram“摆脱人工智能”</title><content type="html"> &lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;“没人想要这个”- 照片通话&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tCWsGEjXJRqdlAkOqUr3qTBabdY=/191x0:5816x3750/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73612081/2172054681.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Tommaso Boddi / Variety via Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;eTKg2k&quot;>;Meta 已经削减了高-演员资料&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/e/24017461&quot;>;将他们的声音&lt;/a>;发送给 Meta AI 聊天机器人，克里斯汀·贝尔 (Kristen Bell) 就是首批声音之一。贝尔的声音让人有点惊讶。早在 6 月份，她就公开表示反对 Meta 的人工智能使用她的数据。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;tg9x9k&quot;>;她转发了一条 Instagram 热门消息，宣称她拒绝同意 Meta 使用她的内容和肖像来训练大语言模特并要求 Instagram“摆脱人工智能程序”。&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class=&quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;Kristen Bell / Instagram&lt;/cite>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;hMzBBr&quot; >;该提示声称，通过重新发布，用户拒绝 Meta 将其个人数据用于这些目的的权限。杰西卡·查斯坦、莎拉·保罗森和阿什丽·提斯代尔等名人 &lt;a href=&quot;https://thetab.com/uk/2024/09/25/what-is-goodbye-meta-ai-post-instagram-hoax-388529 &quot;>;已重新发布此提示的最新版本&lt;/a>; —...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253834/kristen- Bell-meta-ai-voice-connect&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253834/kristen-bell-meta-ai-voice-connect" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24253834/kristen-bell-meta-ai-voice-connect</id><author><name>凯莉罗宾逊</name></author></entry></feed>